### State Management: `analysisStore.ts`

**Location:** [analysisStore.ts](file:///home/edelweiss/Program/pythonProject/TATrendingTopic/frontend/src/stores/analysisStore.ts) (246 lines)

Pinia store managing the entire pipeline state:

| State Property | Type | Updated By |
|----------------|------|------------|
| `datasetMeta` | `DatasetMeta \| null` | `fetchDatasetOverview()` |
| `ngrams` | `PaginatedResponse<NGram>` | `fetchNgrams(page)` |
| `edgeList` | `PaginatedResponse<Edge>` | `fetchEdges(page)` |
| `burstAnalysis` | `BurstAnalysis` | `fetchBurstAnalysis(term?)` |
| `networkData` | `NetworkData` | `fetchNetworkData()` |
| `trendResults` | `TrendResult[]` | `fetchTrendSummary()` |
| `currentStep` | `StepId` | `setStep(n)` |
| `pipelineStatus` | `PipelineStatus` | `startPipeline()` |

### Composables

| Composable | Location | Purpose |
