### End-to-End Pipeline (27,207 tweets)

```
Step 1 ✅ Overview:   27,207 tweets │ 9,341 users │ Feb 28 → Apr 26
Step 2 ✅ N-Grams:    10,997 terms  │ Top: israel, perang iran, negara
         Edge List:   17,977 edges  │ 5,662 → 5,066 users (1.5s)
Step 3 ✅ Kleinberg:  179 bursts    │ 30 terms │ Levels 1-2
Step 4 ✅ Anomaly:    200 nodes     │ 663 edges │ Scores: 0.30-0.33
Step 5 ✅ Trends:     30 classified │ All 🟢 organic (correct for real topic)

Top 10 Results:
 #1  🟢  "as"        L2  anomaly=0.320  general
 #2  🟢  "indonesia" L2  anomaly=0.323  general
 #3  🟢  "serikat"   L2  anomaly=0.311  general
 #4  🟢  "negara"    L2  anomaly=0.332  general
 #5  🟢  "selat"     L2  anomaly=0.314  general
 #6  🟢  "trump"     L2  anomaly=0.309  general
 #7  🟢  "dunia"     L2  anomaly=0.314  general
 #8  🟢  "timur"     L2  anomaly=0.318  general
 #9  🟢  "presiden"  L2  anomaly=0.313  politics
 #10 🟢  "minyak"    L2  anomaly=0.319  economy
```
